<P>
<H2>Home Front</H2><P>

<CENTER>Table of Contents</A><p> 
<A HREF="#mender ">Marriage Menders</A><BR>
<A HREF="#div">Divorce Buster</A><BR>
<A HREF="#lang">Language of  Diplomacy</A><BR>
<A HREF="#better">Better Wed Than Dead</A><BR>
<A HREF="#count">Counting the Costs</a><br>
