<TITLE>RICHARD FISHER -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>RICHARD FISHER</H3>
<HR>
<B>SENIOR POLICY ANALYST, ASIAN STUDIES CENTER</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/fisher.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
Fisher specializes in Asian strategic issues, such as the future of U.S. security alliances in Asia and the prospects for promoting U.S.-Asian free trade. He has traveled throughout Asia, where he observed the 1986 Philippine and the 1987 South Korean presidential elections. Fisher graduated from Eisenhower College with a B.A. in international relations.

