<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/heritage/library/categories/budgettax/fyi113.html 204.71.237.80 19970210145139 text/html 17286
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 14:52:26 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 21:11:44 GMT
Content-length: 17102
