Send a <A HREF="mailto:polrev@heritage.org">Letter to the Editor</A> or write our editorial office:<p>
<b><i>Policy Review</i></b>, 214 Massachusetts Avenue, NE, Washington, D.C. 20002. Phone (202) 546-4400, Fax (202) 675-0291.<p>
